node.text: Yes guys anothet German cat review. If you don't like it get, get over it lol. node.text: I've wanted to drive one of these ever since 2007 when they were on the cover of Gran Turismo 5: The Prologue! Finally got the chance! Let me know your thoughts! Is it worth the money? #gtr #nissan #twinturbo

I came to you guys about this in December of last year and January of this about the RPM act! This not a thing to piss off, if you care anything about this industry and our sport of racing or owning modified cars then you NEED TO SPEAK THE F*** UP! (Pardon my French). I've been seeing a lot more people posting about now it now cause they see that it's a real thing, quit wasting time and go this website and fill out the email to send to your representative! https://www.votervoice.net/mobile/SEMA/campaigns/45394/respond
@jp.tuned
